quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  94,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  94,1,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam )kiya hum ne tumhara seenah khol nahi diya? ( be shak khol diya )
  94,2,aur tum par se boojh bhi utaar diya
  94,3,jis ne tumhari peeth toar rakhi thi
  94,4,aur tumhara zikar bulandkiya
  94,5,haan haan mushkil ke sath aasani bhi hai
  94,6,( aur ) be shak mushkil ke sath aasani hai
  94,7,to jab farigh howa karo to ( ibadat mein ) mehnatkiya karo
  94,8,aur apne perwar-digaar ki taraf mutwajjah ho jaya karo
